com.pandora.general.services.calculation.interfaces

Packages that use com.pandora.general.services.calculation.interfaces
Package
Description
com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations
Implementation classes for services related to calculations in PANDORA.
  • Classes in com.pandora.general.services.calculation.interfaces used by com.pandora.general.services.calculation.implementations
    Class
    Description
    CellTimestepService
    The CellTimestepService interface defines methods for calculating the time series of cell timesteps for a given geographical cell.
    FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsService
    The FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsService interface defines a method for creating and returning a set of first-order differential equations for the Pandora model based on the provided PandoraTimestep.
    LocalDateTimeService
    The LocalDateTimeService interface defines methods for performing operations related to LocalDateTime instances in the context of the Pandora model.
    PandoraIntegratorService
    The PandoraIntegratorService interface defines a method for integrating the Pandora model simulation for a given PandoraTimestep.
    ReactionCalculationService
    The ReactionCalculationService interface defines a method for calculating reactions in the Pandora model based on the current state variables.
    RiverTimestepService
    The RiverTimestepService interface defines a method for calculating the next timestep for each cell in the river simulation.
    TransportCalculationService
    The TransportCalculationService interface defines a method for calculating the transport of each species based on the given state variables and discharge rate.
